{{!
    @template quizaccess_announcements/announcement

    An individual announcement, showing the time posted and the announcement content.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * timeposted The formatted string showing the time the announcement was made, displaying using the timezone information of the user.
    * content HTML showing the announcement content.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "timeposted": "1:07 PM",
        "content": "There was a problem with question 5. It should have said pineapple not mushroom."
    }
}}
<div class="quizaccess_announcements_announcement">
    <div class="quizaccess_announcements_time">{{{timeposted}}}</div>
    <div class="quizaccess_announcements_text">{{{content}}}</div>
</div>
